  h2.-text--h2.-text--bold.-mb--1.-mt--3 <a href="https://github.com/CenturyLinkCloud/ux-chi/releases/tag/v2.0.0" target="_blank">Chi v2.0.0</a>
  .-text--grey.-text--md.-mb--1 April 23, 2020
