  #chi-v200-tabs--release-notes.chi-tabs-panel.-active
    .-pt--1
      h3.-text--h3.-text--bold Components
      h4.-text--h4.-text--bold Breaking changes
      ul.-text.-pl--2
        li Renamed: All component class prefixes for consistency with Chi's web component names. (e.g. <code>a-icon</code> is now <code>chi-icon</code>).
        li Renamed: All legacy camel case classes to kebab case (e.g. <code>-floatingLabel</code> is now <code>-floating-label</code>).
        li Renamed: Text utility size classes for consistency (e.g. <code>-text--smaller</code> is now <code>-text--xs</code>).
        li Renamed: Alert close CSS classes from dismiss to close (e.g. <code>m-alert__dismiss-button</code> is now <code>chi-alert__close-button</code>).
        li Renamed: Number Input component container from <code>m-input__wrapper</code> to <code>chi-number-input</code>.
        li Renamed: Number Input Expanded component container from <code>m-inputNumber</code> to <code>chi-number-input -expanded</code>.
        li Changed: Number Input sizes (e.g. <code>-sm</code>) are now declared on the component container <code>chi-number-input</code> instead of the input.
        li Changed: Card content <code>chi-card__content</code> now displays as flex column by default for consistency with primary use cases. Flex column utility classes no longer need to be applied.
      h4.-text--h4.-text--bold Added
      ul.-text.-pl--2
        li Added: Icons to support Enterprise ticketing portal use cases (<code>icon-filter</code>, <code>icon-flag</code>, <code>icon-paste</code>).
        li Added: Consistent 508/WCAG compliant focus state to all Form components and Buttons.
        li Added: Sizing utility now supports width increments of 5% for more control over Enterprise Portal table columns (e.g. <code>-w--45</code>).
        li Added: Skeleton loaders to web components which provide users with an indication that content is loading.
        li Added: Popover now supports footers to store actions such as links and buttons.
        li Added: Breadcrumb now supports five size classes (e.g. <code>-xs</code>, <code>-sm</code>) to render the component larger or smaller.
        li Added: Tabs now support the ability to mark specific tab links as disabled with class <code>-disabled</code>.
        li Added: Text utility heading size classes <code>-text--h1</code> - <code>-text--h6</code> to render text with h1-h6 heading tag styles.
        li Added: Card content now supports the child element <code>chi-card__caption</code> as a more consistent way of storing card captions.
        li Added: Card now supports the class <code>-align--center</code> to flex center align all child elements for Enterprise Portal KPI style cards.
        li Added: Card now supports the class <code>-hover--animate</code> to animate a KPI style card on hover.
        li Added: Card now supports the class <code>-no-border</code> to render cards without a border.
        li Added: Button now supports turning off <code>-flat</code> button hover states with the class <code>-no-hover</code>.
      h4.-text--h4.-text--bold Changed
      ul.-text.-pl--2
        li Changed: Checkbox and Radio Button border width for better consistency with Consumer and Enterprise Portal use cases.
        li Changed: Button base hover and active state color for better consistency with Consumer and Enterprise Portal use cases.
        li Changed: Sidenav has adopted Enterprise Portal's design as the base design for the component. Specifying the class <code>-global-nav</code> is no longer necessary.
        li Changed: Pagination styles have been updated for better consistency with Enterprise Portal use cases.
        li Changed: Progress component base color from semantic green to primary blue for brand consistency.
        li Changed: Date picker dates in calendar now render with a normal font-weight when unselected, and a semi-bold font-weight when selected.
        li Changed: Date picker web component now renders icons using Chi's Icon web component.
        li Changed: Card footers now space buttons automatically using a CSS adjacent sibling combinator.
        li Changed: Alert and Popover web component (beta) mutation observer.
        li Changed: Drawer web component (beta) is now closable by default (primary use case). Added support for <code>non-closable</code> property to render without a close button.
        li Renamed: Alert web component (beta) close property from <code>dismissible</code> to <code>closable</code> for consistency.
        li Renamed: Alert web component (beta) no border property from <code>borderless</code> to <code>no-border</code> for consistency.
        li Renamed: Drawer web component (beta) no header property from <code>headless</code> to <code>no-header</code> for consistency.
        li Renamed: Expansion Panel web component (beta) title property from <code>heading</code> to <code>title</code> for consistency.
      h4.-text--h4.-text--bold Fixed
      ul.-text.-pl--2
        li Fixed: Dropdown bug which failed to toggle some dropdowns using the data-target method.
        li Fixed: Date picker web component bug which caused 24px of whitespace to render below the input.
        li Fixed: Sidenav behavior when menu items have no association to a Drawer.
        li Fixed: Sidenav IE11 compatibility issues.
        li Fixed: Accessibility warning in Drawer web component due to skipped heading level.
        li Fixed: Accessibility error in Number Input web component due to missing label.
        li Fixed: Expansion Panel step numbers did not hide all step number related margins on xs viewports.
        li Fixed: Expansion Panel step numbers could not be turned off on all viewports without the use of margin utilities.
        li Fixed: Expansion Panel -bordered panels rendered large gap of whitespace between header and content.
        li Fixed: Picker Groups with icons were rendered with a 4px smaller height than those without icons.
        li Fixed: Picker height was inconsistent with height of size class -md (base size).
        li Fixed: Alert icons rendering squished on small viewports.
        li Fixed: File Input button padding was not consistent with button component.

      h3.-text--h3.-text--bold Documentation
      h4.-text--h4.-text--bold Breaking changes
      ul.-text.-pl--2
        li Changed: Consolidated all documentation from /javascript and /custom-elements sections into /components to improve usability.
      h4.-text--h4.-text--bold Added
      ul.-text.-pl--2
        li Added: Designed new introduction page to better explain Chi and what it provides.
        li Added: Tabs to all documentation code samples that allow toggling between blueprint code and framework code.
        li Added: Property tab to each component page to store properties, events, methods, and more.
        li Added: Accessibility tab to each component page to store accessibility guidelines and best practices.
        li Added: CenturyLink favicon to Documentation website.
        li Added: Drawer documentation example to illustrate the use of the title property.
        li Added: Text Utilities have been updated with new documentation for text sizes and headings.
        li Added: Card examples that illustrate new behavior: No border, Align center, Animate on hover.
      h4.-text--h4.-text--bold Changed
      ul.-text.-pl--2
        li Changed: Removed Icon SVG sprite method (chi-icons.js) from Icon page in favor of Web Component and Web Font methods.
        li Changed: Unified icons in all documentation examples with web fonts for HTML Blueprints and web component icons for Web Components.
        li Changed: Popover documentation has been updated with new examples.
        li Changed: Moved Development Workflow information to dedicated page within Getting Started.
        li Changed: Documentation content containers from divs to more semantic tags (<code>main</code>, <code>nav</code>, <code>header</code>, <code>article</code>).
        li Changed: Improved component descriptions for Date picker, Expansion panel, Icon, Popover, and Grid.
        li Changed: Improved invalid form examples for Text Input, Textarea, and Select.
      h4.-text--h4.-text--bold Fixed
      ul.-text.-pl--2
        li Fixed: Styles and logic for anchoring headings within documentation pages.
        li Fixed: Bug related to -active class management when navigating to an anchor element within documentation tabs.
        li Fixed: Some Expansion Panel documentation code samples did not match examples.
        li Fixed: Corrected several classes on the Text Utilities page which included a period.

